author: kencall
body:
The new 1x1 HF trigger primitives are saved in the same collection as the 3x2 HF trigger primitives.
All of the existing trigger primitive plots are retained; however, new plots have been defined which use exclusively the 3x2 or 1x1 tigger primitives.

plots labled *v0 use the 3x2 trigger primitives
plots labled *v1 use the 1x1 trigger primitives
title: Produces Hcal Digi plots where the HF TPs are separated between 3x2 and 1x1 TPs
